{"id":17524,"date":"2022-06-30T11:48:25","date_gmt":"2022-06-30T04:48:25","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/theplannersvn.com\/?p=17524"},"modified":"2022-11-09T13:36:34","modified_gmt":"2022-11-09T06:36:34","slug":"halong-and-6-reasons-to-hold-your-wedding-here","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/theplannersvn.com\/halong-and-6-reasons-to-hold-your-wedding-here\/","title":{"rendered":"6 Great Reasons To Hold Your Wedding In Halong"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-1 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-id=\"17277\" src=\"https:\/\/theplannersvn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/sunset.jpeg\" alt=\"Halong Bay\" class=\"wp-image-17277\" srcset=\"https:\/\/theplannersvn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/sunset.jpeg 1200w, https:\/\/theplannersvn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/sunset-768x512.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-stackable-columns stk-block-columns stk-block stk-d9d5efb\" data-block-id=\"d9d5efb\"><style>.stk-d9d5efb{padding-top:3em !important;padding-right:3em !important;padding-bottom:3em !important;padding-left:3em !important;margin-bottom:0% !important}@media screen and (max-width:1024px){.stk-d9d5efb{padding-top:3em !important;padding-right:3em !important;padding-bottom:3em !important;padding-left:3em !important;margin-bottom:0px !important}}@media screen and (max-width:767px){.stk-d9d5efb{padding-top:0em !important;padding-right:0em !important;padding-bottom:0em !important;padding-left:0em !important;margin-bottom:0px !important}}<\/style><div class=\"stk-row stk-inner-blocks stk-block-content stk-content-align stk-d9d5efb-column\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-stackable-column stk-block-column stk-block-column--v2 stk-column stk-block stk-853ce3c\" data-block-id=\"853ce3c\"><style>@media screen and (max-width:1025px){.stk-853ce3c-container{margin-top:20px !important;margin-right:0px !important;margin-bottom:20px !important;margin-left:0px !important}}<\/style><div class=\"stk-column-wrapper stk-block-column__content stk-container stk-853ce3c-container stk--no-background stk--no-padding\"><div class=\"stk-block-content stk-inner-blocks stk-853ce3c-inner-blocks\">\n<p>Among various ideal destinations in Vietnam for couples to celebrate their big day such as Danang, Nha Trang, Hoi An,\u2026 there is a rising choice to hold romantic and unique weddings \u2013 the charming coastal city of Halong. Long been known as the top tourism center of the country, Halong has proven itself as a prominent location for both destination and city weddings with its numerous natural and cultural advantages. A beautiful city with lovely people and breathtaking landscapes, there is no doubt Halong should be at the top of your list for your wedding weekend. Let us walk you through 5 great reasons to hold your wedding in this amazing city!<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"has-text-align-center wp-block-heading\" id=\"1-wonderful-natural-landscape\">1. Wonderful natural landscape<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-2 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-id=\"17245\" src=\"https:\/\/theplannersvn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10dayVietnam4-1563961581-4041-1563961635_1200x0.jpeg\" alt=\"-\" class=\"wp-image-17245\" srcset=\"https:\/\/theplannersvn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10dayVietnam4-1563961581-4041-1563961635_1200x0.jpeg 1200w, https:\/\/theplannersvn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10dayVietnam4-1563961581-4041-1563961635_1200x0-768x512.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-stackable-columns stk-block-columns stk-block stk-c930ffa\" data-block-id=\"c930ffa\"><style>.stk-c930ffa{padding-top:3em !important;padding-right:3em !important;padding-bottom:3em !important;padding-left:3em !important;margin-bottom:0% !important}@media screen and (max-width:1024px){.stk-c930ffa{padding-top:3em !important;padding-right:3em !important;padding-bottom:3em !important;padding-left:3em !important;margin-bottom:0px !important}}@media screen and (max-width:767px){.stk-c930ffa{padding-top:0em !important;padding-right:0em !important;padding-bottom:0em !important;padding-left:0em !important;margin-bottom:0px !important}}<\/style><div class=\"stk-row stk-inner-blocks stk-block-content stk-content-align stk-c930ffa-column\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-stackable-column stk-block-column stk-block-column--v2 stk-column stk-block stk-726b8af\" data-block-id=\"726b8af\"><style>@media screen and (max-width:1025px){.stk-726b8af-container{margin-top:20px !important;margin-right:0px !important;margin-bottom:20px !important;margin-left:0px !important}}<\/style><div class=\"stk-column-wrapper stk-block-column__content stk-container stk-726b8af-container stk--no-background stk--no-padding\"><div class=\"stk-block-content stk-inner-blocks stk-726b8af-inner-blocks\">\n<p>Needless to say, as one of Vietnam\u2019s most prestigious and long-time tourism center, Halong possesses what could truly be the most unique natural wonder of the world \u2013 Halong Bay. Recognized as a World\u2019s Natural Heritage Site by UNESCO, this is the main attraction of Halong City and Quang Ninh Province, giving tourists and couples the oohs and ahhs while they are cruising in its stunning sceneries. Comprising thousands of islands and limestone karsts in all shapes and sizes, the astonishing views of the Bay alone could grab any couple\u2019s attention to both hold their wedding and spend the honeymoon weekend here.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-3 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" data-id=\"17542\" src=\"https:\/\/theplannersvn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Halong-Bay.jpeg\" alt=\"-\" class=\"wp-image-17542\" srcset=\"https:\/\/theplannersvn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Halong-Bay.jpeg 1920w, https:\/\/theplannersvn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Halong-Bay-768x512.jpeg 768w, https:\/\/theplannersvn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Halong-Bay-1536x1024.jpeg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-stackable-columns stk-block-columns stk-block stk-0306e91\" data-block-id=\"0306e91\"><style>.stk-0306e91{padding-top:3em !important;padding-right:3em !important;padding-bottom:3em !important;padding-left:3em !important;margin-bottom:0% !important}@media screen and (max-width:1024px){.stk-0306e91{padding-top:3em !important;padding-right:3em !important;padding-bottom:3em !important;padding-left:3em !important;margin-bottom:0px !important}}@media screen and (max-width:767px){.stk-0306e91{padding-top:0em !important;padding-right:0em !important;padding-bottom:0em !important;padding-left:0em !important;margin-bottom:0px !important}}<\/style><div class=\"stk-row stk-inner-blocks stk-block-content stk-content-align stk-0306e91-column\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-stackable-column stk-block-column stk-block-column--v2 stk-column stk-block stk-a3297b2\" data-block-id=\"a3297b2\"><style>@media screen and (max-width:1025px){.stk-a3297b2-container{margin-top:20px !important;margin-right:0px !important;margin-bottom:20px !important;margin-left:0px !important}}<\/style><div class=\"stk-column-wrapper stk-block-column__content stk-container stk-a3297b2-container stk--no-background stk--no-padding\"><div class=\"stk-block-content stk-inner-blocks stk-a3297b2-inner-blocks\">\n<p>Cat Ba Island, Sung Sot Cave, Monkey Island, Floating Village,\u2026 are among the endless must-visit attractions of the Bay with magnificent exotic landscapes. These scenic places will definitely capture your heart!<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-4 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1400\" height=\"974\" data-id=\"17540\" src=\"https:\/\/theplannersvn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Baia-di-Halong-Vietnam-2.jpeg\" alt=\"-\" class=\"wp-image-17540\" srcset=\"https:\/\/theplannersvn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Baia-di-Halong-Vietnam-2.jpeg 1400w, https:\/\/theplannersvn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Baia-di-Halong-Vietnam-2-768x534.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"has-text-align-center wp-block-heading\" id=\"2-pleasant-weather-all-year-round\">2. Pleasant weather all year round<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-5 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1360\" height=\"910\" data-id=\"17216\" src=\"https:\/\/theplannersvn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/vinh-ha-long-viet-nam.jpeg\" alt=\"-\" class=\"wp-image-17216\" srcset=\"https:\/\/theplannersvn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/vinh-ha-long-viet-nam.jpeg 1360w, https:\/\/theplannersvn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/vinh-ha-long-viet-nam-768x514.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1360px) 100vw, 1360px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-stackable-columns stk-block-columns stk-block stk-815f021\" data-block-id=\"815f021\"><style>.stk-815f021{padding-top:3em !important;padding-right:3em !important;padding-bottom:3em !important;padding-left:3em !important;margin-bottom:0% !important}@media screen and (max-width:1024px){.stk-815f021{padding-top:3em !important;padding-right:3em !important;padding-bottom:3em !important;padding-left:3em !important;margin-bottom:0px !important}}@media screen and (max-width:767px){.stk-815f021{padding-top:0em !important;padding-right:0em !important;padding-bottom:0em !important;padding-left:0em !important;margin-bottom:0px !important}}<\/style><div class=\"stk-row stk-inner-blocks stk-block-content stk-content-align stk-815f021-column\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-stackable-column stk-block-column stk-block-column--v2 stk-column stk-block stk-63ff7ec\" data-block-id=\"63ff7ec\"><style>@media screen and (max-width:1025px){.stk-63ff7ec-container{margin-top:20px !important;margin-right:0px !important;margin-bottom:20px !important;margin-left:0px !important}}<\/style><div class=\"stk-column-wrapper stk-block-column__content stk-container stk-63ff7ec-container stk--no-background stk--no-padding\"><div class=\"stk-block-content stk-inner-blocks stk-63ff7ec-inner-blocks\">\n<p>As a coastal city located in a region blessed by Mother Nature of Vietnam, this region has a subtropical climate with pleasant weather all year long. The average temperature is 23.5\u00b0C (74.39\u00b0F), its summer is not frustratingly hot while winter is dry and cool. The sun always shines brightly but rarely scorching hot, so you can enjoy your wedding trip in this coastal city without having to worry about sweating excessively.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-6 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1280\" data-id=\"17297\" src=\"https:\/\/theplannersvn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/699007.jpeg\" alt=\"-\" class=\"wp-image-17297\" srcset=\"https:\/\/theplannersvn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/699007.jpeg 2048w, https:\/\/theplannersvn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/699007-768x480.jpeg 768w, https:\/\/theplannersvn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/699007-1536x960.jpeg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-stackable-columns stk-block-columns stk-block stk-d0f84ea\" data-block-id=\"d0f84ea\"><style>.stk-d0f84ea{padding-top:3em !important;padding-right:3em !important;padding-bottom:3em !important;padding-left:3em !important;margin-bottom:0% !important}@media screen and (max-width:1024px){.stk-d0f84ea{padding-top:3em !important;padding-right:3em !important;padding-bottom:3em !important;padding-left:3em !important;margin-bottom:0px !important}}@media screen and (max-width:767px){.stk-d0f84ea{padding-top:0em !important;padding-right:0em !important;padding-bottom:0em !important;padding-left:0em !important;margin-bottom:0px !important}}<\/style><div class=\"stk-row stk-inner-blocks stk-block-content stk-content-align stk-d0f84ea-column\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-stackable-column stk-block-column stk-block-column--v2 stk-column stk-block stk-49fab00\" data-block-id=\"49fab00\"><style>@media screen and (max-width:1025px){.stk-49fab00-container{margin-top:20px !important;margin-right:0px !important;margin-bottom:20px !important;margin-left:0px !important}}<\/style><div class=\"stk-column-wrapper stk-block-column__content stk-container stk-49fab00-container stk--no-background stk--no-padding\"><div class=\"stk-block-content stk-inner-blocks stk-49fab00-inner-blocks\">\n<p>Although Halong is not significantly impacted by storms or hurricanes, you should consider not holding your wedding here from May to October, since they are the rain season in this region. The best time to come here is between February to May and October to early December, when the weather is perfect for outdoors events.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"has-text-align-center wp-block-heading\" id=\"3-top-tourism-center-in-vietnam\">3. Top tourism center in Vietnam<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-7 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-id=\"17527\" src=\"https:\/\/theplannersvn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Ha_Long_2019_taken_by_DJI_FC220-1.jpeg\" alt=\"-\" class=\"wp-image-17527\" srcset=\"https:\/\/theplannersvn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Ha_Long_2019_taken_by_DJI_FC220-1.jpeg 1200w, https:\/\/theplannersvn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Ha_Long_2019_taken_by_DJI_FC220-1-768x512.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-stackable-columns stk-block-columns stk-block stk-0c95230\" data-block-id=\"0c95230\"><style>.stk-0c95230{padding-top:3em !important;padding-right:3em !important;padding-bottom:3em !important;padding-left:3em !important;margin-bottom:0% !important}@media screen and (max-width:1024px){.stk-0c95230{padding-top:3em !important;padding-right:3em !important;padding-bottom:3em !important;padding-left:3em !important;margin-bottom:0px !important}}@media screen and (max-width:767px){.stk-0c95230{padding-top:0em !important;padding-right:0em !important;padding-bottom:0em !important;padding-left:0em !important;margin-bottom:0px !important}}<\/style><div class=\"stk-row stk-inner-blocks stk-block-content stk-content-align stk-0c95230-column\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-stackable-column stk-block-column stk-block-column--v2 stk-column stk-block stk-7bf1b2a\" data-block-id=\"7bf1b2a\"><style>@media screen and (max-width:1025px){.stk-7bf1b2a-container{margin-top:20px !important;margin-right:0px !important;margin-bottom:20px !important;margin-left:0px !important}}<\/style><div class=\"stk-column-wrapper stk-block-column__content stk-container stk-7bf1b2a-container stk--no-background stk--no-padding\"><div class=\"stk-block-content stk-inner-blocks stk-7bf1b2a-inner-blocks\">\n<p>Holding your wedding in a tourism city like Halong certainly has its edge, namely accommodation and entertainment. There are various high-class hotels and resorts which provide professional services and luxurious amenities for you and your significant other to spend a meaningful and exciting wedding weekend or honeymoon at.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-stackable-columns stk-block-columns stk-block stk-f955e52\" data-block-id=\"f955e52\"><style>.stk-f955e52{padding-top:0px !important;padding-right:0px !important;padding-bottom:0px !important;padding-left:0px !important;margin-bottom:20px !important}@media screen and (max-width:1024px){.stk-f955e52{margin-top:10px !important}}@media screen and (max-width:767px){.stk-f955e52{margin-bottom:20px !important}}<\/style><div class=\"stk-row stk-inner-blocks stk-block-content stk-content-align stk-f955e52-column\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-stackable-column stk-block-column stk-block-column--v2 stk-column stk-block stk-9f5df70\" data-block-id=\"9f5df70\"><style>.stk-9f5df70-container{display:flex !important}.stk-9f5df70-inner-blocks{justify-content:center !important}.stk-9f5df70-container{flex-direction:column !important}.stk-9f5df70-container{margin-right:6em !important;margin-left:5em !important}@media screen and (max-width:1025px){.stk-9f5df70-container{margin-top:0px !important;margin-right:20px !important;margin-bottom:0px !important;margin-left:0px !important}}@media screen and (max-width:767px){.stk-9f5df70-container{margin-top:0px !important;margin-right:0px !important;margin-bottom:20px !important;margin-left:0px !important}}<\/style><div class=\"stk-column-wrapper stk-block-column__content stk-container stk-9f5df70-container stk--no-background stk--no-padding\"><div class=\"stk-block-content stk-inner-blocks stk-9f5df70-inner-blocks\">\n<p>In addition to that, the city offers exciting activities for couples and their guests  before and after the wedding. Its cuisine is one of its signature charms \u2013 a food tour would be a wonderful idea when you explore the city at night. You can taste different seafood dishes made from marine animals that you might have never seen before.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-stackable-column stk-block-column stk-block-column--v2 stk-column stk-block stk-8803fb8\" data-block-id=\"8803fb8\"><style>.stk-8803fb8-container{margin-top:0px !important;margin-right:0px !important;margin-bottom:0px !important;margin-left:10px !important}@media screen and (max-width:1025px){.stk-8803fb8-container{margin-top:0px !important;margin-right:0px !important;margin-bottom:0px !important;margin-left:0px !important}}@media screen and (max-width:767px){.stk-8803fb8-container{margin-top:0px !important;margin-right:0px !important;margin-bottom:0px !important;margin-left:0px !important}}<\/style><div class=\"stk-column-wrapper stk-block-column__content stk-container stk-8803fb8-container stk--no-background stk--no-padding\"><div class=\"stk-block-content stk-inner-blocks stk-8803fb8-inner-blocks\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"379\" src=\"https:\/\/theplannersvn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/ha-long-cuisine-1_1652861181.jpeg\" alt=\"-\" class=\"wp-image-17529\"><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-8 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"790\" height=\"444\" data-id=\"17531\" src=\"https:\/\/theplannersvn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Floating-village-Halong-culture-min.jpeg\" alt=\"-\" class=\"wp-image-17531\" srcset=\"https:\/\/theplannersvn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Floating-village-Halong-culture-min.jpeg 790w, https:\/\/theplannersvn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Floating-village-Halong-culture-min-768x432.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 790px) 100vw, 790px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1260\" height=\"681\" data-id=\"17533\" src=\"https:\/\/theplannersvn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/visitvietnam-3.jpeg\" alt=\"-\" class=\"wp-image-17533\" srcset=\"https:\/\/theplannersvn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/visitvietnam-3.jpeg 1260w, https:\/\/theplannersvn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/visitvietnam-3-768x415.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1260px) 100vw, 1260px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-9 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1170\" height=\"400\" data-id=\"17535\" src=\"https:\/\/theplannersvn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Nightlife-in-Halong-Bay.jpeg\" alt=\"-\" class=\"wp-image-17535\" srcset=\"https:\/\/theplannersvn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Nightlife-in-Halong-Bay.jpeg 1170w, https:\/\/theplannersvn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Nightlife-in-Halong-Bay-768x263.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1170px) 100vw, 1170px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-stackable-columns stk-block-columns stk-block stk-692e642\" data-block-id=\"692e642\"><style>.stk-692e642{padding-top:3em !important;padding-right:3em !important;padding-bottom:3em !important;padding-left:3em !important;margin-bottom:0% !important}@media screen and (max-width:1024px){.stk-692e642{padding-top:3em !important;padding-right:3em !important;padding-bottom:3em !important;padding-left:3em !important;margi